CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Gencor Industries Inc and its subsidiaries is a manufacturer of heavy machinery used in the production of highway construction materials and environmental control equipment. The firm's principal products include asphalt plants, combustion systems, and fluid heat transfer systems.
